{
    "headline": "<h2>Gameplay Features</h2>",
    "content": "<p>Are you ready to play with some power? The 6x4 grid of 5 Lucky Lions offers 88 fixed paylines to give you more chances to win big. Don't worry if you're a low roller, you can start with a minimum bet of €0.01 per line and still have a great time. Want to bet big and feel like a high roller? Go for the maximum bet of €88 and see what happens!</p><p>Do you like to live life in the fast lane? The lightning symbol in the lower left corner of the screen will satisfy your need for speed by accelerating the reel speed. And if you need a break from clicking the spin button, just switch on the auto-spin function and get up to 500 automatic spins. </p><p>With an RTP of 96.79%, there's plenty of opportunities to strike lucky. So, why not give the 5 Lucky Lions a spin and see if you can become a jungle king or queen? Don't be a scaredy-cat, come and play today!</p>"
